PAGE 1 — SERVICES (PRIMARY)
Headline

Kitchen Transformations, Without the Chaos

Subheadline

Premium cabinet refacing, plus full kitchen and bath remodeling through trusted Arizona partners — faster, cleaner, and done right.

Positioning Statement

Vulpine Homes exists to modernize Arizona kitchens intelligently. We specialize in cabinet refacing — the fastest, most cost‑effective way to achieve a high‑end transformation — and coordinate full kitchen and bath remodels through licensed partners when a project calls for more. One streamlined process. One accountable point of contact. Zero unnecessary disruption.

Primary CTA

Plan My Kitchen Upgrade

Service 1 — Cabinet Refacing (Our Specialty)

Cabinet refacing is the smartest upgrade for homeowners who like their layout but want a completely new look. Instead of tearing everything out, we replace doors and drawer fronts, apply a premium matching veneer to your existing cabinet frames, and upgrade hardware — delivering a like‑new kitchen in days, not months.

Why Arizona Homeowners Choose Refacing

Completed in 3–5 days

40–70% less than full replacement

No demolition dust or weeks without a kitchen

Soft‑close hinges and modern hardware standard

Finishes selected for Arizona heat, sun, and daily use

This is what we do best — fast, precise, and built to last.

CTA: Explore Cabinet Refacing

Service 2 — Kitchen & Bath Remodeling (Through Trusted Partners)

Some projects require more than refacing. When walls move, layouts change, or bathrooms need full reconstruction, Vulpine coordinates the project through licensed remodeling partners — including Freedom Kitchen & Bath.

We stay in our lane and manage the process so homeowners don’t have to juggle contractors, timelines, and decisions. You get expert execution, clear communication, and a remodel that actually finishes on schedule.

Ideal For:

Full kitchen remodels

Bathroom renovations

Structural or layout changes

Homeowners who want one coordinated experience

CTA: Discuss a Full Remodel

Service 3 — Architectural Wall Panels & Interior Accents

For homeowners who want more character, we offer architectural wall panels and interior accent upgrades. These are design‑driven enhancements — not trends — used to add warmth, depth, and visual structure to living spaces.

From slat walls to full feature panels, installations are clean, precise, and finished quickly.

CTA: View Wall Panel Options

