PAGE 3 — ABOUT VULPINE HOMES
Headline

Built to Do Things Better

Origin Story

Vulpine Homes was founded in 2025 after recognizing a pattern in the home remodeling industry: unnecessary delays, bloated costs, disconnected labor, and homeowners caught in the middle.

Instead of doing everything, Vulpine chose to do the right things exceptionally well.

By mastering cabinet refacing and building strong partnerships with licensed remodeling teams, we created a system that delivers high‑quality results faster, cleaner, and with far less friction — for homeowners, partners, and crews alike.

What We Believe

Efficiency is a form of respect

Specialization beats generalization

Great results come from great coordination

Homeowners deserve clarity, not confusion

Built for Arizona Homes

Arizona presents unique challenges — intense sun, heat, dust, and daily wear. Every material, finish, and process we use is selected with the Valley in mind. We bring samples into your home so decisions are made in real lighting, not a showroom guess.

The Vulpine Difference

We don’t chase trends or overload homeowners with options. We guide decisions, streamline execution, and stay accountable from first conversation to final install.

That’s how kitchen upgrades should work.

CTA: Start Your Project